OL,7,FA burnt-out caravan has been cordoned
OL,8,Foff in Bristol after a suspected arson
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Ffire on Goodneston Road, on the border
OL,13,Fof Fishponds and Speedwell, at around
OL,14,F5:20pm on Monday, 5 January.
OL,16,FThe road is one of several locations
OL,17,Fin the city with a van-dwelling
OL,18,Fcommunity.
