OL,7,FOne caravan was destroyed in the
OL,8,Fincident, and a second was damaged.
OL,9,FPolice say no one was injured and a
OL,10,Fcordon remains in place at the scene.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Avon Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service said: "Firefighters
OL,14,Fused two breathing apparatus, two high-
OL,15,Fpressure hose reels and two triple
OL,16,Fextension ladders to extinguish the
OL,17,Ffire.
OL,19,F"The cause of the fire was believed to
OL,20,Fhave been deliberate."
