OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police say CCTV and
OL,8,Fhouse-to-house enquiries have been
OL,9,Fcarried out, and crime scene
OL,10,Finvestigators have been on site.
OL,11,FOfficers remain in the area.
OL,13,FNeighbourhood Inspector Richard Jones
OL,14,Fadded: "We are aware of recent
OL,15,Fincidents on this stretch of road, and
OL,16,Fwe are now working with partner
OL,17,Fagencies to improve the area.
