OL,7,F"While we are not linking this
OL,8,Fincident to others recently,
OL,9,Freassurance patrols will be carried
OL,10,Fout, and we are now appealing for
OL,11,Fwitnesses and anybody with information
OL,12,Fto come forward."
OL,14,FThe force is asking those with CCTV,
OL,15,Fdashcam, or doorbell footage,
OL,16,Fimmediately before and after the
OL,17,Fincident, to contact them quoting
OL,18,Freference 5226003914.
