OL,7,FThe council said it is "working
OL,8,Ftowards finding a new and sustainable
OL,9,Fsolution to the growing number of
OL,10,Fpeople living in vehicles across the
OL,11,Fcity", as tensions with neighbours
OL,12,Frise in some locations.
OL,14,FAt the Downs in particular, protests
OL,15,Fhave been held and complaints have
OL,16,Fbeen made about the impact of people
OL,17,Fliving at the much-loved green space.
OL,18,FWork began last month to remove van
OL,19,Fdwellers from the location.
