OL,7,FIn November the council issued a
OL,8,Fstatement asserting it will "continue
OL,9,Fto take action where necessary".
OL,10,FThough the statement largely referred
OL,11,Fto the Downs, it also referenced the
OL,12,Fremoval of one abandoned caravan and
OL,13,Fone abandoned vehicle from Goodneston
OL,14,FRoad.
